OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Simeon
OL,4,CMayou
OL,6,FSimeon Mayoy, Age: 99, Royal Navy
OL,7,FPatrol Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 20 February 2024
OL,11,FOn board HMS Fusilier on D-Day, Mr
OL,12,FMayou was a radar operator who'd
OL,13,Fpreviously been escorting Atlantic
OL,14,Fconvoys.
OL,16,FThe ship was a heavily-armed naval
OL,17,Ftrawler and told to head to the
OL,18,FChannel ports.
