OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Simeon
OL,4,CMayou
OL,6,FMr Mayou said: "It was a very good
OL,7,Fship, and our job had been searching
OL,8,Ffor U-boats.
OL,10,F"It was a brand new ship, and it was
OL,11,Fbuilt in the style of trawlers.
OL,13,F"We came to the Channel and it was a
OL,14,Fhuge sight to see - we thought the
OL,15,FBritish Navy was going to have a
OL,16,Fbattle with the German Navy.
OL,18,F"On 6th of June over our PA came the
OL,19,Forder for all non-duty ratings to form
OL,20,Fon the main mess deck.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
