OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Simeon
OL,4,CMayou
OL,6,F"Just free-firing with a big gun,"
OL,7,FSimeon added.
OL,9,F"After a while we were told to cease
OL,10,Ffiring because we were almost hitting
OL,11,Four own troops.
OL,13,F"The big gunners were enjoying
OL,14,Fthemselves at that time. It was a very
OL,15,Floud noise when it went off.
OL,17,F"We came off the beach area and the
OL,18,Fnext job was to escort big tank
OL,19,Flanding craft which were being used as
OL,20,Fan emergency vehicle to get the
OL,21,Fseriously wounded back to Portsmouth.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
