OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Simeon
OL,4,CMayou
OL,6,F"Germany was still operating those one-
OL,7,Fman submarines so we were to escort
OL,8,Fthese people back."
OL,10,FOn arrival, Mr Mayou was one of those
OL,11,Fchosen to act as a stretcher bearer.
OL,13,FLater in Normandy he was involved in
OL,14,Fthe rescue of survivors from a ship
OL,15,Fwhich had been mined, ferrying them to
OL,16,Fa hospital ship.
